1.0.name: wordpress/seo-meta-tags
1.0.description:
You can enter your meta keywords and description for your homepage.
This plugin will add different Meta description for each individual post as your excerpt of your post. This will help your blog to rank better in google. You can easily increase your blog traffic using this plugin. digcms.com

Tested upto 2.9.2

Functionality

This plugin will add differnt Meta description for each individual post as your excerpt of your post.
